text: Jung Nam-suk is a South Korean taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in bantamweight at the 1989 World Taekwondo Championships in Seoul, by defeating Chen Yi-an in the semifinal, and Diane Murray in the final. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:South Korean female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
